<p>The Faculty of Health and Sport Sciences at University of Tsukuba in Japan will organize a workshop to celebrate the International Day of Sport for Development and Peace on April 6th. </p><p>This event will be a ground for sharing ideas and creativities among students and staffs, and a good start of the new master’s courses in International Development and Peace through Sport which will be starting this year at the university.</p><p>Learn more <a href="http://www.april6.org/en/play-your-peace/upcoming-events/sport-for-development-and-peace-workshop.html">here</a></p><p></p>